exceptions.exn: In environment x : Rbar P : R -> Prop Unable to unify "match ?M2363 with | Finite a => locally' a P | p_infty => exists M : R, forall x : R, M < x -> P x | m_infty => exists M : R, forall x : R, x < M -> P x end" with "match x with | Finite a => locally a P | p_infty => exists M : R, forall x : R, M < x -> P x | m_infty => exists M : R, forall x : R, x < M -> P x end".
